Open the file `index.html`.

Locate the entire contact form block starting with:

    <input type="text" value=""/>

and ending with:

    <button>Send request</button>

Delete that entire block.

Replace it with the following fully working Formspree-backed form:

    <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mwpjldlb" method="POST" style="display: grid; gap: 1rem;">

      <input type="hidden" name="form_id" value="website-contact" />
      <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Statycal consultation request" />
      <input type="hidden" name="recipient" value="hello@statycal.com" />

      <label>
        Name
        <input type="text" name="name" required autocomplete="name" />
      </label>

      <label>
        Work email
        <input type="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" />
      </label>

      <label>
        Company
        <input type="text" name="company" autocomplete="organization" />
      </label>

      <label>
        What do you need help with?
        <select name="topic" required>
          <option value="">Choose an area</option>
          <option value="Data & Analytics">Data & Analytics</option>
          <option value="Cloud & Infrastructure">Cloud & Infrastructure</option>
          <option value="Cybersecurity">Cybersecurity</option>
          <option value="Automation & AI">Automation & AI</option>
          <option value="Pricing/Engagement">Pricing/Engagement</option>
        </select>
      </label>

      <label>
        Message
        <textarea name="message" required></textarea>
      </label>

      <button type="submit" class="btn primary full">
        Send request
      </button>

    </form>

Save the file.
